subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description:
Such procedures include capturing data on the parties involved in the case, schedule hearings and preparing hearings notices, recording documents received by the court, preparing hearing and minutes, judicial orders and judgments
MIZAN also produce reports on aggregate caseload useful to court managers and supreme judicial council executives and allocating court resources and special studies on operation of courts.
MIZAN version 1 is currently in the process of being upgraded. MIZAN version 2 is expected to include more advanced features and link with prosecution.
